{"tid":1926554,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【武漢肺炎】消息指法籍男子初步確診　為化妝品牌 Sephora 創辦人兒子　法國回港　","createTime":"2020-03-15T07:57:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T11:03:57.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"dfd91582fd2f6e887a0efa06e82b47288f14ac29","tid":1926554,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T07:57:07.000Z","msg":"武漢新型冠狀病毒疫情持續，有醫護人員向《立場新聞》透露，將軍澳醫院今日錄得一宗初步陽性個案，病人曾與朋友到法國巴黎遊覽，再由法國返港。有醫護人員表示，病人是法籍男子。<br />\n<br />\n若病人最終確診，本港累計個案將會增至 143 宗。<br />\n<br />\n有醫護人員透露，病人是歐洲化妝及香水連鎖店Sephora創辦人的兒子Thierry Mandonnaud。根據Sephora官方網頁，公司於1992年併入LVMH Group，在全球29個國家擁有1900間分店，其中亞太區有200多間分店，包括澳洲、中國、新加坡、馬來西亞、泰國等地。"},{"pid":"1965fb05f6a0488eb4a8b8b378f8712bc97528b2","tid":1926554,"uid":346806,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T08:01:39.000Z","msg":"走黎香港做乜9"},{"pid":"07aa958b4c2728946455b4b5df963dc49edc4399","tid":1926554,"uid":99172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T08:42:30.000Z","msg":"Sephora 創辦人個仔住將軍澳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c29dbbf72b6417e36fd90ed630f641258a0c7813","tid":1926554,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T10:47:38.000Z","msg":"唔識"},{"pid":"d4a6ae2afb98b69faf2f3ce280c248f9bef3d421","tid":1926554,"uid":17081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T10:48:47.000Z","msg":"呢啲無謂嘢醫護就識透露<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef58c9295b482797a81a1c149baa6bbaa56479f8","tid":1926554,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T10:49:43.000Z","msg":"今次真係法唔法國post系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d79d0ef455235666c3aa85b6132c70c5ea974e5a","tid":1926554,"uid":271617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1965fb05f6a0488eb4a8b8b378f8712bc97528b2","tid":1926554,"uid":346806,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,